screen_desc: A screenshot of a social media app's menu page. The top section displays the user's profile picture and name, with an option to create a new profile or page. Below, there are several menu options including Memories, Saved, Groups, Video, Marketplace, Friends (25 online), Feeds, and Dating. At the bottom, there are expandable sections for Help & support and Settings & privacy. The top bar shows icons for Home, Videos, Marketplace, Notifications, and Menu. The time and various status icons are visible at the very top.
